{"tid":1525292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不安到瞓唔著 黎互相打打氣！","createTime":"2019-08-31T21:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:19:23.000Z","uid":261767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"993c0752eb5ba161c7e1184d503e0d05b85f9260","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:46:34.000Z","msg":"幾時完...自從斬人 同出真槍 個人成日都勁焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出親門口都好不安 會成日覺得有人隨時打我車死我咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">大家黎互相打打氣喇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5c58bfec121fb2f2b1086969cab31d61fa3875ef","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:47:52.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"fbeaac685d4605a832777fad3634c087eb80f0df","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:48:02.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"6c355498b45d0269c42cc58c4ac299cf26103420","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"1c8c0ff8f3bcf9275790b27865c7b7483b040a7a","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:49:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"357411cba517796488164d4beacdbec712fe8e25","tid":1525292,"uid":90318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b490882c607c40bcb8ad4425e184ccef095f87a","tid":1525292,"uid":289041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:51:33.000Z","msg":"我都瞓唔著。。"},{"pid":"09fc1d344f3c97a12879d29ea7de9bf6138f432d","tid":1525292,"uid":314614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357411cba517796488164d4beacdbec712fe8e25","tid":1525292,"uid":90318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b790f090d21579bbe9e633c39a6beaeb18c8a264","tid":1525292,"uid":55770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:57:34.000Z","msg":"Same here..情緒好差"},{"pid":"6fa22a9687819f08c99bf869987c4ae812e40ddf","tid":1525292,"uid":260315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:59:22.000Z","msg":"我喊醒咗............<br />\n琴晚走到前所未有咁前，俾狗圍，見到手足俾狗咬，救唔到佢，好自責，我覺得自己苟且偷生。<br />\n啱啱我發夢，係室內俾狗咬，俾狗圍，係狗車俾人用腳玩心口，俾人用大光燈射，但係我叫唔到出聲，最後我喊醒咗.....原來一切都是夢<br />\n<br />\n我寧願死，我寧願死係戰場，都唔想做戰俘<br />\n<br />\n心好累，仲要發幾多次夢？<br />\n<br />\n我想要返香港，用3萬隻狗加個阿婆換，唔夠？豪多一班無恥賣港賊。唔好再用手足既血汗換啦"},{"pid":"6bcfb48d2ce5a4b73a36d5b60e768c2456550590","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09fc1d344f3c97a12879d29ea7de9bf6138f432d","tid":1525292,"uid":314614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357411cba517796488164d4beacdbec712fe8e25","tid":1525292,"uid":90318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76811a27ab50052f43d0ccecff64b355e9fd39db","tid":1525292,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:02:38.000Z","msg":"心痛您們一班手足。多謝您地，黑警已失性，家務必要萬事小心。<br />\n如果好焦慮，暫時抖一抖先，路好漫長，我地要一齊行落去。"},{"pid":"ab88d9a9e1e52966f8ce8a603bbe8f8a6a02a58c","tid":1525292,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76811a27ab50052f43d0ccecff64b355e9fd39db","tid":1525292,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:02:38.000Z","msg":"心痛您們一班手足。多謝您地，黑警已失性，家務必要萬事小心。<br />\n如果好焦慮，暫時抖一抖先，路好漫長，我地要一齊行落去。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:07:26.000Z","msg":"大家要抖足精神<br />\n再繼續行依條崎嶇既路"},{"pid":"f30460056cdaf0d9776c057dec32791edfc2c2be","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:09:45.000Z","msg":"我唔敢做前線 專登去學急救想有啲貢獻 睇警察落閘嗰吓唔俾first aid 救人 好似廢埋我個人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddc144da26ec0722c2580104f77540cdffc4209","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:14:21.000Z","msg":"有咩唔開心嘅情緒大家記得搵人傾下 抖一抖再一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9749747d144b0c4bb3d615640dcc3335f4c3d2f9","tid":1525292,"uid":27561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:56:40.000Z","msg":"加油？<br />\n我今世最討的一個辭語。<br />\n叫春？<br />\n今日去狗鐵拆閘機啦"},{"pid":"14a695280a53ff43d3e540eb2717512fff34bea7","tid":1525292,"uid":290468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:32:26.000Z","msg":"殘忍d講句，唔會咁快完，一係長期白色恐怖，一係支港共出盡全力打爆我地，摧毀運動，係依個時候每個人要心理生理上都更好裝備自己，準備好全民皆兵全面抗爭既一日，果一日真係不遠"},{"pid":"783d67f31056d3b66b3aa26bf0083ec181eababe","tid":1525292,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993c0752eb5ba161c7e1184d503e0d05b85f9260","tid":1525292,"uid":261767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:46:34.000Z","msg":"幾時完...自從斬人 同出真槍 個人成日都勁焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出親門口都好不安 會成日覺得有人隨時打我車死我咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">大家黎互相打打氣喇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=a6acfea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}